Path: godot/classes/class_editorproperty.rst
Summary: This section lists the properties available for EditorProperty, including their types, names, and default values.

Properties:
* checkable (bool): Default: false
* checked (bool): Default: false
* deletable (bool): Default: false
* draw_background (bool): Default: true
* draw_label (bool): Default: true
* draw_warning (bool): Default: false
* focus_mode (FocusMode): Default: 3 (overrides Control.focus_mode)
* keying (bool): Default: false
* label (String): Default: ""
* name_split_ratio (float): Default: 0.5
* read_only (bool): Default: false
* selectable (bool): Default: true
* use_folding (bool): Default: false
